    {
      "id": "race_elan",
      "category": "race",
      "ruleSource": "srd_psionics",
      "label": {
        "en": "Elan",
        "fr": "Élan"
      },
      "description": {
        "en": "Elans are aberrations that look exactly like humans. They are former humans who were transformed into a new type of being through a secret psionic process performed by existing elans. Unlike most aberrations, elans do not have darkvision. Their unique psionic nature gives them the ability to spend power points for defensive effects: resistance to attacks, damage reduction, and sustenance.",
        "fr": "Les élans sont des aberrations qui ressemblent exactement à des humains. Ce sont d'anciens humains transformés en un nouveau type d'être par un processus psionique secret. Leur nature psionique unique leur permet de dépenser des points de pouvoir pour des effets défensifs : résistance aux attaques, réduction des dégâts et sustentation."
      },
      "tags": [
